tags.note: Name suspicious. Unclearly defined by signs in Mapillary: N end has no name sign, but instead ref. sign to Bavnehøjvej 4 (+maybe to Arielvej? Picture unclear). In S end, at T/Y junctions with Krakevej/Jasonvej/Garmvej, no signs visible in Mapillary.
